core.controller.mediatypes

Class LDMediaTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.ws.rs.core.MediaType
      • core.controller.mediatypes.LDMediaTypes

  • public class LDMediaTypes
extends javax.ws.rs.core.MediaType
    Extends the MediaType with prefdefined media types that are neccessary for LD-Communication. See w3.org for further information. https://www.w3.org/2008/01/rdf-media-types
    Author:
    Jan-Peter.Schmidt
